{"legislative_session": "119", "identifier": "HRES 1014", "title": "Providing for consideration of the bill (H.R. 7148) making further consolidated appropriations for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2026, and for other purposes; providing for consideration of the bill (H.R. 7147) making further consolidated appropriations for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2026, and for other purposes; and for other purposes.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["resolution"], "subject": [], "abstracts": [], "other_titles": [], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-us-119-hres1014"}], "actions": [{"description": "Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.", "date": "2026-01-22T16:52:34+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On agreeing to the resolution, as amended Agreed to by recorded vote: 214 - 213 (Roll no. 41).", "date": "2026-01-22T16:52:32+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Passed/agreed to in House: On agreeing to the resolution, as amended Agreed to by recorded vote: 214 - 213 (Roll no. 41).", "date": "2026-01-22T16:52:32+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["passage"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On ordering the previous question on the amendment and the resolution Agreed to by the Yeas and Nays: 215-213 (Roll no. 39).", "date": "2026-01-22T16:06:45+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered as unfinished business. (consideration: CR H1183-1185)", "date": "2026-01-22T15:31:11+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on H. Res. 1014, the Chair put the question on ordering the previous question on the amendment and the resolution and by voice vote, announced the ayes had prevailed. Mr. McGovern demanded the yeas and nays and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.", "date": "2026-01-22T15:16:10+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on H. Res. 1014.", "date": "2026-01-22T14:22:02+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered as privileged matter. (consideration: CR H1177-1183; text: CR H1177)", "date": "2026-01-22T14:17:21+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 56.", "date": "2026-01-22T05:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 7148 under a structured rule and H.R. 7147 under a closed rule. The rule provides for one hour of debate and a motion to recommit on each bill.", "date": "2026-01-22T14:03:25+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The House Committee on Rules reported an original measure, H. Rept. 119-462, by Ms. Foxx.", "date": "2026-01-22T05:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}], "sponsorships": [{"name": "Virginia Foxx", "classification": "primary", "entity_type": "person", "primary": true, "person_id": "~{\"name\": \"Virginia Foxx\"}", "organization_id": null}], "related_bills": [{"identifier": "HR 7148", "legislative_session": "119", "relation_type": "companion"}, {"identifier": "HR 71